Robot head that uses a Raspberry Pi as the controller.

Unit has the following moving parts

1. Two webcam eyes with up/down and left/right movement
2. Eyelids
3. Eyebrows
4. Two degree of freedom neck
5. Small VGA screen to provide mouth
6. TTS and audio playback for voice and sound
7. IR and ultrasonic sensor to detect visitors

Jim Herd
2013
